Source: xf86-video-fbdev
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Tux Mason <tuxmason@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), xorg-server-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://xorg.freedesktop.org/

Package: xf86-video-fbdev
Section: libs
Architecture: ARCH
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: X.Org Video Driver for framebuffer devices
 This package provides the X.Org Video Driver for framebuffer 
 devices. This driver is often used as fallback driver if the 
 hardware specific and VESA drivers fail to load or are not 
 present.

Package: xf86-video-fbdev-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Priority: optional
Depends: xf86-video-fbdev (= ${binary:Version})
Recommends: man-db
Description: X.Org framebuffer video driver documentfbdevon
 This package provides man pages for the X.Org framebuffer
 video driver.
